00:33:02,840 --> 00:33:06,660
 Isu li ispunio svoje poslanje?

685
00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:07,640
 Isu uopće shvatio

686
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:08,700
 koje je tvoje poslanje?

687
00:33:08,700 --> 00:33:10,620
 Isu li ovdje na zemlji

688
00:33:10,620 --> 00:33:12,220
 samo da bi uživoo?

689
00:33:15,820 --> 00:33:18,960
 Mislim da nam fali jedna doza ozbiljnosti,

690
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:20,920
 bez odbira koliko smo stari ili mladi.

691
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:23,300
 Bog je svet.

692
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:24,760
 Savršen.

693
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:27,340
 Svet i savršen.

694
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:31,200
 I služi se nama slabim, grešnim ljudima.

695
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,980
 I Bog

696
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:35,840
 bira one koji će mu reći

697
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:36,940
 da, Bože, idem.

698
00:33:36,940 --> 00:33:39,700
 Idem, a šta god ti traži od mene.

699
00:33:39,700 --> 00:33:40,280
 Idem.

700
00:33:40,280 --> 00:33:42,500
 Nekako je nama cilj postalo

701
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:43,640
 da se zabavimo,

702
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,480
 da se oženim,

703
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:45,340
 dobijem djecu

704
00:33:45,340 --> 00:33:47,720
 i to je to.

705
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:48,960
 I šta sad?

706
00:33:48,960 --> 00:34:00,680
 Stvarno,

707
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:03,060
 nekad me srce boli.

708
00:34:03,060 --> 00:34:07,000
 Nekad me srce boli

709
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:07,460
 kad vidim

710
00:34:07,460 --> 00:34:10,120
 toliko ljudi

711
00:34:10,120 --> 00:34:12,320
 trči u pakao.

712
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:13,960
 Trči u pakao.

713
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:19,120
 A ja niš ne radim po tom pitanju.

714
00:34:21,640 --> 00:34:23,840
 Ne moram ja ići odmah govoriti svim ljudima o

715
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:25,480
 o Bogu.

716
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:26,940
 Ali, Bože, pripremi me

717
00:34:26,940 --> 00:34:29,020
 da jednog dana budem neustrašiv.

718
00:34:29,020 --> 00:34:31,580
 Pa mi je oko i živimo u Bosni i Hercegovini.

719
00:34:31,580 --> 00:34:34,240
 Pa 50% ljudi su muslimani.

720
00:34:34,240 --> 00:34:38,320
 Šta misliš kom će te Bog slati?

721
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:41,020
 I šta će reći

722
00:34:41,020 --> 00:34:42,660
 među iliz islamske zajednice

723
00:34:42,660 --> 00:34:45,500
 kad se muslimani krenu obraćati preko tebe?

724
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:48,500
 Oće li govoriti lijepo o tebi?

725
00:34:48,500 --> 00:34:49,600
 Če te prozivati?

726
00:34:49,600 --> 00:34:51,480
 Jesi smo spremni na to?

727
00:34:51,640 --> 00:34:53,560
 Pa nije šala.

728
00:34:53,560 --> 00:34:55,880
 Ja sam i moja ljuda

729
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,140
 tako dođu na posao

730
00:34:57,140 --> 00:35:00,000
 i bolesni.

731
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:01,780
 I u meni odmah

732
00:35:01,780 --> 00:35:03,900
 želja

733
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:05,260
 da se molim za njih.

734
00:35:05,260 --> 00:35:07,000
 I jedna muslimanka

735
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:09,600
 rekao, dje dođe sjedi, rekao,

736
00:35:09,600 --> 00:35:12,380
 da se pomolim za tebe ako hoćeš.

737
00:35:12,380 --> 00:35:13,260
 Uma kao može.

738
00:35:13,260 --> 00:35:15,300
 I ona je sjela

739
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:16,640
 i ja sam krenio moliti

740
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:19,320
 i završao sam molitvu kratko.

741
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:20,700
 I ona kaže,

742
00:35:21,140 --> 00:35:22,500
 osjećajam kao da je nešto ošlo s mene.

743
00:35:22,500 --> 00:35:24,000
 Pa rekao, je.

744
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:26,640
 I ja joj navijestim Isusa

745
00:35:26,640 --> 00:35:29,060
 i kažem joj da je Isus Bog, jedini, jedini Bog.

746
00:35:30,980 --> 00:35:34,520
 i odtad nema baš neku predobru komunikaciju,

747
00:35:34,520 --> 00:35:36,480
 ali ja sam se svoj odradio.

748
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:41,320
 Ja nisam naviješto svojom udrošću.

749
00:35:43,220 --> 00:35:44,460
 rekao, Bog te dotako.

750
00:35:44,460 --> 00:35:48,460
 I stvarno me Bog vodi u te neke situacije,

751
00:35:48,460 --> 00:35:50,780
 da vam ne pričam, sad stvarno,

752
00:35:50,780 --> 00:35:53,120
 jako neugodne, jako nezgodne.

753
00:35:54,660 --> 00:35:55,980
 I kad god sam izmako,

754
00:35:55,980 --> 00:35:58,880
 ponovno sam bio u toj situaciji.

755
00:35:58,880 --> 00:36:00,600
 Kad god sam se povuko,

756
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:02,800
 ponovno sam došao u tu situaciju.

757
00:36:03,160 --> 00:36:04,660
 I Bog te neće pustiti dalje

758
00:36:04,660 --> 00:36:07,380
 dok ne prođeš kroz tu situaciju.

759
00:36:07,380 --> 00:36:10,520
 I to je kršćanstvo.

760
00:36:10,520 --> 00:36:12,300
 To je kršćanstvo.

761
00:36:12,300 --> 00:36:13,760
 Nema tu,

762
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:16,300
 mislim, ima tu radosti.

763
00:36:16,300 --> 00:36:18,080
 Ali radost kad ti

764
00:36:18,080 --> 00:36:20,360
 vidiš da se neko mijenja,

765
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:21,700
 da si promijenio nekom život,

766
00:36:21,700 --> 00:36:23,640
 da si donio nekom Boga,

767
00:36:23,640 --> 00:36:25,560
 i tad si radostan.

768
00:36:25,560 --> 00:36:27,660
 Tati ne može niko skiniti osmijeg slica.

769
00:36:27,660 --> 00:36:29,120
 Ja sam još uvijek bolestan,

770
00:36:29,120 --> 00:36:30,040
 ali mi je sve jedno.

771
00:36:30,040 --> 00:36:32,280
 Znači sve jedno mi je za bolest.

772
00:36:32,540 --> 00:36:33,540
 Absolutno sve jedno.

773
00:36:33,540 --> 00:36:36,420
 Ma na ono, do kraja života

774
00:36:36,420 --> 00:36:38,080
 ja sam toliko obišao mjesta

775
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:40,600
 i pomazanika se Boži molilo za mene

776
00:36:40,600 --> 00:36:41,460
 i da mi ja šteni.

777
00:36:41,460 --> 00:36:43,200
 Ne znam, u Gršku smo išli.

778
00:36:43,200 --> 00:36:44,220
 Ma ne, gdje nismo išli.

779
00:36:44,220 --> 00:36:46,200
 I na kraju primim odgovor.

780
00:36:46,200 --> 00:36:49,100
 Bolje ti je ući u raj,

781
00:36:49,100 --> 00:36:51,860
 bez noge ili bez ruke.

782
00:36:51,860 --> 00:36:53,880
 I ja onako,

783
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:56,160
 rekao Bože,

784
00:36:56,160 --> 00:36:58,200
 pa ja sam mislio da sam ja malo bolji.

785
00:36:58,200 --> 00:37:01,060
 Ja sam mislio da sam ja tebi vjeran.

786
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:02,020
 Ja sam nešto postigo.

787
00:37:02,420 --> 00:37:05,720
 i ja sam shvatio da nisam nigdje.

788
00:37:05,720 --> 00:37:08,060
 Da nisam ni počeo kako treba.

789
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:12,340
 i sve je Božja milost.

790
00:37:12,340 --> 00:37:13,400
 Rekao Bože, hvala ti.

791
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:15,880
 Hvala ti što ja to mogu sad prihvatiti.

792
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:17,880
 Što ja to mogu prihvatiti.

793
00:37:19,340 --> 00:37:23,740
 i svaka teška situacija je Božja ljubav sad u tvojem životu.

794
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:25,180
 Kako god da je teška,

795
00:37:25,180 --> 00:37:27,980
 Bog ti iskaže ljubav kroz tu situaciju.

796
00:37:27,980 --> 00:37:30,860
 i želite osnažiti,

797
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:32,640
 želite ojačati,

798
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:35,020
 jer vremena koja dolaze nisu za šalu.

799
00:37:36,440 --> 00:37:37,840
 uopće nisu za šalu.

800
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:40,060
 Mogle bi plakat sad šta nas čeka.

801
00:37:40,820 --> 00:37:42,140
 i bolje da ne znamo šta nas čeka.

802
00:37:42,140 --> 00:37:46,020
 Ali kad te Bog provodi kroz nešto,

803
00:37:46,020 --> 00:37:47,560
 ne opiri se,

804
00:37:47,560 --> 00:37:49,440
 nego uživaj,

805
00:37:49,440 --> 00:37:50,340
 zahvaljuj,

806
00:37:50,340 --> 00:37:51,820
 promijeni svoj pogled.

807
00:37:51,820 --> 00:37:55,120
 Znači, loše situacije su dobre.

808
00:37:56,460 --> 00:37:57,740
 Ono što mi mislimo da je loše,

809
00:37:57,740 --> 00:38:00,660
 ako si predao svoj život Bogu

810
00:38:00,660 --> 00:38:01,980
 i ne živiš u teškom grijehu,

811
00:38:01,980 --> 00:38:04,020
 Bog te vodi.

812
00:38:04,020 --> 00:38:06,020
 Bog te vodi

813
00:38:06,020 --> 00:38:07,600
 i kušate.

814
00:38:07,600 --> 00:38:09,120
 Zlato se u vatri čisti.

815
00:38:09,120 --> 00:38:10,820
 Zlato se u...

816
00:38:10,820 --> 00:38:12,880
 I vi ste svi zlata vrijedni,

817
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:14,580
 dragocjeni u Božijim očima.

818
00:38:14,580 --> 00:38:17,020
 I nemojte izmicat vatri,

819
00:38:17,020 --> 00:38:18,860
 nemojte izmicat teškim situacijama.

820
00:38:18,860 --> 00:38:20,860
 I ako sad živiš

821
00:38:20,860 --> 00:38:25,040
 i nisi u svoj volji,

822
00:38:25,540 --> 00:38:26,820
 ništa ne ide po tvom planu,

823
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:27,880
 slavi Boga.

824
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:30,400
 Slavi Boga.

825
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:32,600
 Što ništa ne ide po tvom planu.

826
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:34,920
 Jer znači da ide po njegovom.

827
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:38,120
 Znači da ide po njegovom.

828
00:38:38,120 --> 00:38:42,540
 I stvarno vam želimo hrabriti da...

829
00:38:42,540 --> 00:38:45,920
 da ustrajete

830
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:48,040
 i da nikad ne uzmaknite.

831
00:38:48,040 --> 00:38:50,140
 I kad vas Bog potiše na nešto,

832
00:38:50,140 --> 00:38:53,780
 skoči, skoči u to.

833
00:38:54,620 --> 00:38:55,500
 Skoči.

834
00:38:55,500 --> 00:38:59,680
 Jer jednog dana ćemo doći pred Božije lice i...

835
00:38:59,680 --> 00:39:04,000
 Da li ćemo se puno kajati

836
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:05,460
 ili malo kajati,

837
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:06,800
 o nama ovisi.

838
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:08,680
 Ali ćemo se kajati sigurno.

839
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:10,780
 Sto posto ćemo se kajati.

840
00:39:10,780 --> 00:39:14,220
 Evo, vrijeme mi je isteklo.

841
00:39:14,220 --> 00:39:15,760
 Mislili smo moliti,

842
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:17,000
 ali nećemo moliti,

843
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:18,100
 pošto nemamo vremena.

844
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:21,000
 Tako da, evo, vidimo se poslije.

